{"tid":756224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【肥妹變索復仇】新劇《Insatiable》被轟物化女性 12萬人聯盟促停播","createTime":"2018-07-26T01:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T12:37:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ff5c78c4593c51e262f1d1c0fb4cac36f20489","tid":756224,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:09:23.000Z","msg":"Netflix將於8月首播新劇《Insatiable》，講述由Debby Ryan飾演嘅中學生Patty原本係肥妹仔一名，受盡同學欺凌，點知一日突然間變瘦成為一名靚女，然後佢一心想展開復仇計劃。劇情引來部份女生不滿，直指劇情對女性造成羞辱，繼續灌輸年輕女性為吸引男性，或者要成功，一定要保持窈窕體型嘅觀念，譴責劇情助長女性身體被物化，發起聯署運動，要求Netflix停播《Insatiable》，現時已有超過12萬網民簽名支持。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/090859_e7a309644ea8d10e77df74f4bbc0dc8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F090859_e7a309644ea8d10e77df74f4bbc0dc8e.png&h=6f2c995d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/090859_22b6d095358d39b97a2172a9671a9806.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F090859_22b6d095358d39b97a2172a9671a9806.png&h=3ee34b61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/090900_35090880a3f8d0486af061ea890072a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F090900_35090880a3f8d0486af061ea890072a3.png&h=c170f728&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/090901_0d316a2c4385290b3cb28351e0f73627.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F090901_0d316a2c4385290b3cb28351e0f73627.png&h=148bbb37&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/090902_0d316a2c4385290b3cb28351e0f73627.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F090902_0d316a2c4385290b3cb28351e0f73627.